OL,7,F"This place is a godsend and it's
OL,8,Fliterally a lifesaver for some people.
OL,9,FYou can't put a price on what they do
OL,10,Fhere."
OL,12,FIt's been three months since Michael
OL,13,Fcame to the hostel on Manvers Street
OL,14,Fin.
OL,16,FHe's 47 and worked all his life until
OL,17,Fjust a few years ago, when he found
OL,18,Fhimself sleeping rough in a tent, with
OL,19,Fonly his French bulldog Bubbles for
OL,20,Fsupport.
