OL,3,C'Without this place, I wouldn't be
OL,4,Chere' - Man says budget cuts will cost
OL,5,Clives
OL,7,F"She was my best friend, my protector,
OL,8,Fand living rough - as you can imagine
OL,9,F- she was my alarm too," he said.
OL,11,FBut at the start of 2023, a group of
OL,12,Fdrunk people attacked Michael in his
OL,13,Ftent at night.
OL,15,F"They tent-bombed my tent, I don't
OL,16,Fknow if they knew I was in there or
OL,17,Fnot, and unfortunately they stood on
OL,18,FBubbles.
OL,20,F"They actually broke her back and she
OL,21,Fwas squealing from the pain.
