OL,3,C'Without this place, I wouldn't be
OL,4,Chere' - Man says budget cuts will cost
OL,5,Clives
OL,7,F"I came out of the tent to defend her
OL,8,Fand managed to fight off one of them
OL,9,Fand then I got hit with a bottle from
OL,10,Fbehind.
OL,12,F"They stamped all over me, knocked my
OL,13,Fteeth out and pretty much left me for
OL,14,Fdead on the floor. A dog walker found
OL,15,Fme in the morning and she called the
OL,16,Fambulance and the police."
OL,18,FMichael moved in with his sister for a
OL,19,Ffew months, but he soon realised the
OL,20,Fattack had left him with mental and
OL,21,Fphysical scars.
