OL,3,C'Without this place, I wouldn't be
OL,4,Chere' - Man says budget cuts will cost
OL,5,Clives
OL,7,F"It left me with PTSD and anxiety,
OL,8,Fbecause I kept reliving it night after
OL,9,Fnight. I'd wake up the house because
OL,10,FI'd be screaming and shouting and
OL,11,Ffighting in my sleep.
OL,13,F"I had two broken teeth from the
OL,14,Fattack, which had become infected, but
OL,15,FI couldn't get a dentist's appointment
OL,16,Fthrough 111."
