OL,4,Chere' - Man says budget cuts will cost
OL,5,Clives
OL,7,FSo Michael went to Julian House, a
OL,8,FBath charity that support people
OL,9,Fexperiencing homelessness, escaping
OL,10,Fdomestic abuse, adults with learning
OL,11,Fdifficulties and people who need
OL,12,Fsupport after leaving prison.
OL,14,FHe managed to get a spot in their
OL,15,Fhomeless hostel and within a month
OL,16,Fthey put him on a dental plan. Since
OL,17,Fthen, the charity has helped him "in
OL,18,Fso many ways".
