OL,3,C'Without this place, I wouldn't be
OL,4,Chere' - Man says budget cuts will cost
OL,5,Clives
OL,7,F"They've helped me with mental health,
OL,8,Fthey put me on a 12-week course with
OL,9,FBath Mind to come to terms with some
OL,10,Fstuff that happened to me as a child.
OL,12,F"They've got me on DHI as well,
OL,13,Ftalking about alcohol abuse, drug
OL,14,Fabuse, mental health - all of the
OL,15,Fthings that come with a rough life on
OL,16,Fthe streets," Michael said.
OL,18,FIn fact, if he hadn't sought help from
OL,19,FJulian House, there's a real chance
OL,20,FMichael wouldn't be here today.
