OL,3,C'Without this place, I wouldn't be
OL,4,Chere' - Man says budget cuts will cost
OL,5,Clives
OL,7,F"Eight months ago I tried to take to
OL,8,Fmy own life and I was dead for a
OL,9,Fminute and a half and they brought me
OL,10,Fback on the third try with the paddles.
OL,12,F"If it wasn't for this place, I don't
OL,13,Fknow where I'd be right now," he said.
OL,15,FPotential cuts on the horizon
OL,17,FSo Michael was "disheartened and
OL,18,Fdisgusted" to learn that Bath and
OL,19,FNorth East Somerset Council has
OL,20,Fproposed reducing its funding for
OL,21,Fadult services in the district.
