OL,5,Clives
OL,7,FRoanne Wootten, strategic partnerships
OL,8,Fdirector at Julian House, said
OL,9,Fcharities in Bath were "on a cliff-
OL,10,Fedge of cuts".
OL,12,FShe said: "These cuts, if approved,
OL,13,Fwill impact our supported housing and
OL,14,Foutreach services, as well as other
OL,15,Fproviders like Bath Mind and
OL,16,FStepChange (debt charity).
OL,18,F"They're proposing cutting the total
OL,19,Fbudget by 34% and it's very unclear at
OL,20,Fthe moment how those cuts will be
OL,21,Fdecided."
