OL,4,Chere' - Man says budget cuts will cost
OL,5,Clives
OL,7,FShe added that, although BANES Council
OL,8,Fhas a statutory duty to try to prevent
OL,9,Fhomelessness and to provide housing
OL,10,Fadvice, it does not have to provide
OL,11,Fsupported housing and outreach
OL,12,Fservices.
OL,14,FThe council needs to save #2.3million
OL,15,Fon adult services this year, which
OL,16,Fmeans that while some providers could
OL,17,Freceive a funding boost, others could
OL,18,Freceive less funding.
OL,20,FAnd any cuts could be catastrophic for
OL,21,FJulian House, Roanne explained.
