OL,4,Chere' - Man says budget cuts will cost
OL,5,Clives
OL,7,F"Previously, we'd see people who had
OL,8,Fcome from very difficult home
OL,9,Fsituations, like they'd come from care
OL,10,For real trauma in their lives.
OL,12,F"We're seeing more and more people who
OL,13,Fare sleeping in their cars, who have
OL,14,Flost their job and their relationship
OL,15,Fand their home all at the same time.
OL,17,F"We're now in a situation where people
OL,18,Fwho have previously been in full-time
OL,19,Femployment in well-known companies are
OL,20,Fending up homeless."
