OL,12,Fcuts has been really hard for our
OL,13,Fclients.
OL,15,F"They cannot understand why their home
OL,16,Fis potentially going to be at risk in
OL,17,Fthe future, why their support worker
OL,18,Fmight not be there anymore."
OL,20,FAnd, in time, people like Michael may
OL,21,Fhave nowhere to go.
